## Your Task

Compare the iterations and identify what was learned across all runs.

## Output Format

Respond with a JSON object containing:
- variance_score: 0.0-1.0 measure of output consistency
- confidence: 0.0-1.0 confidence in the aggregated finding
- best_iteration: which run produced the clearest learning (by index)
- pattern: what consistent finding emerged across iterations
- recommendation: whether to accept findings or investigate instability
